videos.description: Florida's Kevarrius Hayes throws down the dunk and then on the next play FSU's PJ Savoy drains the 3-pointer from way outside.
videos.headline: Florida gets a dunk followed by a deep FSU 3

videos.description: Florida State's M.J. Walker gets the pass and knocks down the three while being fouled.
videos.headline: FSU's Walker drains the 3 and is fouled

videos.description: Florida State's Terance Mann tries to throw the lob towards the basket but it ends up going in for a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: FSU's Mann lobs ends up being a 3-pointer

videos.description: Florida State's M.J. walker shakes his defender then finds Trent Forrest for the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Forrest nails 3-pointer after pass from Walker
